## §R3 Negative Filters Requirements

### R3.1 Content Exclusions

**MUST filter out videos containing:**

**Gambling Keywords:**
- "betting", "odds", "casino", "spelbolag", "odds" (Swedish)
- "bet365", "unibet", "betsson", etc (brands)

**Competitor Keywords:**
- Djurgården (rival club)
- Hammarby (rival club)
- Specific rival player names (configurable list)

**Offensive Content:**
- Profanity (Swedish and English)
- Hate speech
- Discriminatory language

**Non-Sports Content:**
- Political content
- Advertising-only content
- Off-topic discussions

### R3.2 Filter Implementation

**MUST:**
- Check all text fields: title, description, caption transcripts
- Use case-insensitive matching
- Support regex patterns for complex filters
- Log filtered content for review (not expose to users)
- Allow manual override by administrators

**MUST NOT:**
- Filter legitimate sports content
- Over-filter (false positives)
- Expose filter rules to public API

**Implementation:** See `negativeFilters.ts` in `supabase/functions/_shared/`

