## §R5 Sport Detection Requirements

### R5.1 Sport Categories

**MUST detect and categorize:**

**Primary:**
- **Football/Soccer** (Fotboll) - Main focus
- **Hockey** (Ishockey)
- **Bandy** (Bandy)

**Secondary:**
- **Handball** (Handboll)
- **Basketball** (Basketboll)
- **Other** (Övrigt) - Catch-all for other sports

### R5.2 Detection Rules

**MUST:**
- Analyze title and description for sport-specific keywords
- Use AI to disambiguate when multiple sports mentioned
- Default to "Football" for AIK-related content (AIK primarily football club)
- Allow manual category override

**Keywords:**
- Football: "fotboll", "allsvenskan", "superettan", "mål", "match"
- Hockey: "ishockey", "SHL", "puck", "målvakt"
- Bandy: "bandy", "bandyallsvenskan", "bandymål"

**MUST NOT:**
- Categorize non-sports content
- Miscategorize due to ambiguous keywords

**Implementation:** See `sportDetection.ts` in `supabase/functions/_shared/`

