## §R6 Membership Tiers Requirements

### R6.1 Tier Definitions

| Tier Name | Numeric ID | Daily Quota | Features | Price |
|-----------|-----------|-------------|----------|-------|
| **free** | 0 | 10 segments/day | Basic feed access, 24h delay | Free |
| **basic** | 10 | 50 segments/day | + Save favorites, no delay | 49 SEK/mo |
| **premium** | 20 | Unlimited | + AI summaries, advanced filters | 99 SEK/mo |
| **enterprise** | 30 | Unlimited | + API access, priority support | Custom |

### R6.2 Quota Enforcement

**MUST:**
- Check quota via `api_public.my_account_state` view
- Block access when quota exceeded
- Reset quota daily at 00:00 UTC
- Display remaining quota to user
- Prompt upgrade when approaching limit

**Formula:**
```sql
has_quota = segments_used_today < segments_quota OR segments_quota = 0
```
(segments_quota = 0 means unlimited)

### R6.3 Feature Gating

**Free Tier:**
- ✅ View segments via `video_segments_feed` (24h delay)
- ✅ Search segments (limited results)
- ❌ Save favorites
- ❌ AI summaries
- ❌ Advanced filters

**Basic Tier:**
- ✅ All Free features
- ✅ No 24h delay
- ✅ Save unlimited favorites
- ❌ AI summaries
- ❌ Advanced filters

**Premium Tier:**
- ✅ All Basic features
- ✅ AI-generated summaries
- ✅ Advanced filters (date range, sport category)
- ✅ Priority processing

**Enterprise Tier:**
- ✅ All Premium features
- ✅ API access (with API key)
- ✅ Priority support
- ✅ Custom integrations

### R6.4 Tier Verification

**MUST:**
- Verify tier on every API request (via JWT claims or `my_account_state`)
- Cache tier info for session duration (max 1 hour)
- Re-verify after subscription changes
- Handle tier downgrades gracefully

**Implementation:** RLS policies on all tables + `api_public.my_account_state` view

